cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH configuration index to an out-of-range value of 1000 will cause the gNB to fail during initialization as the value exceeds the valid range (0-255).
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 配置索引設定為超出範圍的值 1000 會導致 gNB 在初始化期間失敗，因為該值超過有效範圍 (0-255)。
